{"word":"H5892 - עִיר - ʻîyr - eer - Ai","slug":"H5892","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">עִיר</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>ʻîyr"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>eer"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Ai"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05E2;&#x05D9;&#x05E8;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#x05E2;&#x05E8;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#x05E2;&#x05D9;&#x05E8; - &#x201B;&#x0131;&#x0302;yr  &#x201B;a&#x0302;r  &#x201B;a&#x0302;yar</b> - <i>eer, awr, aw-yar'</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/H5782\">H5782</a> a <i>city</i> (a place guarded by <i>waking</i> or a watch) in the widest sense (even of a mere <i>encampment</i> or <i>post</i>): - Ai [from margin], city, court [from margin], town."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H5888\">H5888</a>, <a href=\"#/H5889\">H5889</a>, <a href=\"#/H5893\">H5893</a>, <a href=\"#/H5898\">H5898</a>, <a href=\"#/H5899\">H5899</a>, <a href=\"#/H5905\">H5905</a>"}]}